      $(document).ready(function() {
            //Setup search box
            $('.searchinput').each(function() {
                var default_value = "Site Search";
                $(this).css('color', '#666');
                $(this).focus(function() {
                    if(this.value == default_value) {
                        this.value = '';
                        $(this).css('color', '#333');
                    }
                });        
                $(this).blur(function() {
                    if(this.value == '') {
                        $(this).css('color', '#666');
                        this.value = default_value;
                    }
                });         
                $(this).keypress(function(e) {
                        if(this.value != '') {
                        if(e.which == 13){
                            e.preventDefault();
                            e.stopPropagation();
                            CallSearch();
                        }
                    }
                });                          
            });

            //Setup search button
            $(".button").click(function () { 
                CallSearch();
            });

        });

        //Clear postback cookie and run search
        function CallSearch() {
            var objsearchText = $(".searchinput");
            var searchText;
            if ((objsearchText.val() != "Site Search")&&(objsearchText != null)) {
                searchText = objsearchText.val();
                searchText = searchText.replace(/>/gi, " >");
                searchText = searchText.replace(/</gi, "< ");
                objsearchText.value = searchText;
                
                document.cookie = 'postbackcookie=';
                document.location.href = "http://" + document.domain + "/search/?searchtext=" + searchText.replace('alert', '').replace('confirm', '');                    
            }
        }   
    </script>

<script language=javascript>
    String.prototype.trim = function () {
    return this.replace(/^\s*/, "").replace(/\s*$/, "");
    }


    //  enable/disable Specialization option based on Physician Type selection
    function updatePhysicianType()
    {
        var objSpecialists = document.getElementById("ctl00_ContentPlaceHolder1_MainContentControl1_ctl00_rdoDocTypeSpecialist");
        var objddSpecialist = document.getElementById("ctl00_ContentPlaceHolder1_MainContentControl1_ctl00_ddSpecialist");
        if(objSpecialists.checked)
        {
            objddSpecialist.disabled = false;
            document.getElementById("lblSpecialization").className = "";
        }
        else
        {
            objddSpecialist.disabled = true;
            objddSpecialist.selectedIndex = 0;
            document.getElementById("lblSpecialization").className = "light-grey";
        }
    }
    
    //  enable/disable Keyword Search based on Discipline selection
    function updateDisciplinary()
    {
        var objChkPastFinding = document.getElementById("ctl00_ContentPlaceHolder1_MainContentControl1_ctl00_chkPastFinding");
        var objChkCurrentReferrals = document.getElementById("ctl00_ContentPlaceHolder1_MainContentControl1_ctl00_chkCurrentReferrals");
        var objTxtExtraInfo = document.getElementById("ctl00_ContentPlaceHolder1_MainContentControl1_ctl00_txtExtraInfo");
        
        if (objChkPastFinding.checked || objChkCurrentReferrals.checked)
        {
            objTxtExtraInfo.disabled = false;
            document.getElementById("lblKeyword").className = "";
        }
        else{
            objTxtExtraInfo.disabled = true;
            objTxtExtraInfo.value = "";
            document.getElementById("lblKeyword").className = "light-grey";
        }
    }
    

    
    //  enable/disable FirstName textfield if value exists in firstName
    function updateFirstName()
    {       
        
        var objLastName = document.getElementById("ctl00_ContentPlaceHolder1_MainContentControl1_ctl00_txtLastName");
        var objFirstName = document.getElementById("ctl00_ContentPlaceHolder1_MainContentControl1_ctl00_txtFirstName");
        
        if (objLastName.value.trim().length > 0)
        {
        
            document.getElementById("lblFirstName").className = "";
            objFirstName.disabled = false;
        }
        
    }
    
    //  enable/disable FirstName textfield if value exists in firstName
    function emptyFirstName(objLastName, objFirstName)
    {
        if (objLastName.value.trim().length == 0)
        {
            document.getElementById("lblFirstName").className = "light-grey";
            objFirstName.disabled = true;
            objFirstName.value = "";
        }
    }

   
    
</script>
